SMTP Server: The address of your SMTP server (e.g., smtp.gmail.com).\par
SMTP Port: The port number (e.g., 587 for TLS or 465 for SSL).\par
Connection Security: Choose either SSL/TLS or STARTTLS based on your server requirements.\par
Username: Your email account username.\par
Password: The password for your email account.\par
Priority: Set the priority if you have multiple outgoing mail servers.\par
Test Connection:\par
\par
