Save: Click Save to finalize your settings.\par
\par
Configuring Incoming Mail Server\par
Incoming Mail Servers:\par
\par
Still in the Technical menu, navigate to Incoming Mail Servers.\par
Create a New Incoming Mail Server:\par
\par
Click on Create.\par
Fill in the fields:\par
Description: A name for your incoming mail server.\par
Server Type: Choose IMAP or POP3 based on your preference.\par
Server: Enter the incoming mail server address (e.g., imap.gmail.com for IMAP).\par
