Troubleshooting\par
Connection Issues: If you encounter issues, double-check the SMTP/IMAP settings and ensure your firewall allows the necessary ports.\par
Authentication: Ensure that your email account allows access from third-party applications (you may need to enable \ldblquote Less Secure Apps\rdblquote  for Gmail).\par
Logs: Check the logs for any errors under Settings > Technical > Email > Emails to debug issues.\par
Conclusion\par
By properly configuring your outgoing and incoming mail servers in Odoo 17, you can streamline communication and enhance your workflow. This setup allows you to manage emails directly within the Odoo platform, improving efficiency and collaboration.\par
